{"tid":2335723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣武漢肺炎253天無本土個案破功","createTime":"2020-12-22T05:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T05:39:55.000Z","uid":192517,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"261bfc400acbfaa679c8df1a9df94fd81f0cd78b","tid":2335723,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"新增3例境外移入<br />\n〔記者林惠琴／台北報導〕全球武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情持續升溫，國內幾乎天天新增境外移入，中央流行疫情指揮中心今日公布，再新增3例，另外，掌握有新增確診本土個案，疑與機師在台外出期間的活動有關，下午1點半召開臨時記者會，由指揮官陳時中對外說明。<br />\n<br />\n過去武漢肺炎新增病例均由發言人莊人祥說明，今日由陳時中說明，目前掌握有新增確診本土個案，疑與機師在台外出期間的活動有關，具體內容仍待指揮中心說明為主。上一次國內出現本土個案為4月12日，總計連續253天沒有本土確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3388413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3388413&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=c9a11fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3388413&h=4f0856e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3388413</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">天佑台灣</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}